Products & Services



Looking for Safety Data Sheets (SDS), Product Specification Sheets or Labels by country?
Product Index





















Wholesale


Without fertilizer, we could only produce about half as much food as we do today. As one of the largest global distributors of fertilizer, we have the capacity to produce and market about 10 million tonnes of nitrogen, phosphate and potash – to help growers worldwide increase the quality and quantity of their crops to feed the world.






 








Nitrogen is crucial to plant nourishment and fundamental to life on the planet. It is a key component of chlorophyll, which gives plants their bright green color.









Phosphate stimulates root development and flowering and encourages early crop development.









Potash is required by crops to regulate growth processes, activate enzymes involved in plant growth and help protect against drought and disease.








