Fertilizer






Agrium's fertilizer products provide growers with the essential nutrients they need to make their crops thrive  – so they can produce more high-quality food to meet the growing global demand. Through our Wholesale unit, we produce and market nitrogen, phosphate, potash and sulfate-based crop nutrients. The amount of each nutrient needed to optimize yields depends on the type of soil, the crop being grown, weather conditions and the previous year’s yield. 
Products
Ammonium Phosphate
Ammonium Sulfate
Anhydrous Ammonia
Aqua Ammonia
Calcium Ammonium Nitrate (CAN 17)
Environmentally Smart Nitrogen (ESN)
Merchant Grade Phosphoric Acid (MGA)
Monoammonium Phosphate (MAP)
Muriate of Potash
Super Phosphoric Acid (SPA)
Urea Ammonium Nitrate
Urea
 



 




 






