			Company Description 


			Agrium, Inc. engages in the production and distribution of agricultural products, services, and solutions. It operates through the Retail and Wholesale segments. The Retail segment offers crop nutrients, crop protection products, seed, merchandise and services. The Wholesale segment produces, market...
		


                Agrium, Inc. engages in the production and distribution of agricultural products, services, and solutions. It operates through the Retail and Wholesale segments. The Retail segment offers crop nutrients, crop protection products, seed, merchandise and services. The Wholesale segment produces, markets, and distributes crop nutrients and industrial products. The company was founded on December 21, 1992 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada
            




