Agrium Seeks Acquisitions
May 18 17
Agrium Inc. (TSX:AGU) is seeking acquisitions. Steve Douglas, Senior Vice President and Chief Financial Officer said, “Accretive acquisitions, we think one example is obviously the tuck-ins, but we're constantly on the lookout. We think this merger with PotashCorp qualifies. And we're constantly on the lookout to, on a risk-adjusted basis, expand our footprint and take advantage of what we see as potential opportunities within the market.”


